	â€¢	âœ… Search box filters down checkbox list.
	â€¢	âœ… Checkbox list scrollable (shows ~4 values max).
	â€¢	âœ… Clear button deselects everything.
	â€¢	âœ… All button selects all.
	â€¢	âœ… Apply button applies current selection + search filter.
	â€¢	âœ… Works fully integrated with AG Gridâ€™s filtering system.

